      <title>中国太阳能硅出口量首次超过进口量</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/china-s-exports-of-solar-silicon-outpace-imports-for-first-time</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于太阳能电池板制造商将更多业务转移到海外以应对国内供应过剩的问题，去年中国太阳能行业使用的多晶硅出口量首次超过进口量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/china-s-exports-of-solar-silicon-outpace-imports-for-first-time</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 04:40:49 GMT</pubDate>
